Description:

   This is the special HOLIDAY HARE 1995 EDITION of the ultra-popular
   arcade game Jazz Jackrabbit!  It features FOUR of the best, all-new
   Jazz levels yet, and a rockin' holiday sound track.  The action is
   just as fast and furious as the original Jazz which has won the hearts
   of gamers around the world.

   Jazz Jackrabbit has become one of the most popular scrolling
   PC arcade games ever -- PC Format Magazine gave Jazz the award for
   "Best arcade game of the year!"

   PC Gamer Magazine said Jazz "simply oozes professionalism and
   style... A top quality game by any standards".

John Dvorak in PC Magazine (November 8, 1994) said:

  "Do you like fast-paced hot games such as that Sonic the Hedgehog
  game on the Sega? Look no further than Jazz Jackrabbit--an absolutely
  stunning PC-based arcade-style game every bit as good as anything
  found on a dedicated game machine."

REQUIRES:

  * 386 33-Mhz or faster processor
  * 4 Megabytes of memory
  * VGA graphics

ALSO SUPPORTS:

  * Joystick, Gravis Gamepad
  * Sound Blaster, SB Pro, SB-16, PAS-16, Gravis Ultrasound sound cards

TO GET THE ENTIRE EPIC COLLECTION:

   Vendors, we'll send the entire collection of Epic's shareware games
   on CD-Rom for only $12 + $4 p&h. Federal Express shipping is also
   available at cost in case you're on a deadline.  Just call us toll-free
   to order, 800-972-7434!

   This CD also contains screen shots from all Epic games and large scanned
   artwork for our latest games,  suitable for printing with your 
   packaging and catalogs.

Registration options:

   There are NINE episodes of Jazz Jackrabbit.  Both Episode 1 and both
   special Christmas Editions are shareware.

   You can buy the first SIX episodes of Jazz for $39, or all NINE episodes
   Plus the 1994 Christmas Edition on CD-Rom for just $49! Either way, you
   get a full-color Jazz manual and comic book and a free bonus disk.  Plus,
   you can get a full-color Jazz tee shirt for just $12.  S, M, L,
   and XL sizes are available!

CONCLUSION:  We thank you very much for distributing this game!  The Epic
team looks forward to working with you to promote shareware.

